---
import { SITE, whatsappLink } from "~/lib/config";
---

<section class="py-20 sm:py-28 bg-horno-cream relative overflow-hidden">
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-horno-orange/10 rounded-full blur-3xl -translate-y-1/2 translate-x-1/2"></div>
  <div aria-hidden="true" class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 w-72 h-72 bg-horno-magenta/10 rounded-full blur-3xl translate-y-1/2 -translate-x-1/2"></div>

  <div class="section relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
      <span class="eyebrow">Cupos limitados</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl mb-6">
        Reserva tu <span class="text-horno-magenta">lugar</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-horno-magentaDeep/80 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8">
        Trabajamos con pedidos programados para garantizar frescura y calidad en cada postre.
        Cada semana abrimos cupos limitados para mantener el estándar artesanal que nos distingue.
      </p>

      <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-3 bg-white rounded-full px-6 py-3 shadow-card mb-10">
        <span class="h-3 w-3 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 animate-pulse"></span>
        <span class="font-display text-horno-magentaDeep">
          Cupos de esta semana:
          <span data-target="15" class="counter text-emerald-600">0</span>
        </span>
      </div>

      <div>
        <a
          href={whatsappLink(`¡Hola ${SITE.name}! Quiero reservar un cupo para esta semana.`)}
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
          class="btn-primary"
        >
          Reservar ahora
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  import "~/scripts/counter-animation.js";
</script>

<div class="ornament-divider" aria-hidden="true"></div>
